类 VehicleVendorPermission

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.car.hardware.property.VehicleVendorPermission

  • public final class VehicleVendorPermission
extends java.lang.Object
    VehicleVendorPermission lists all vendor permissions for vehicle. Vendors can map the vendor properties with any vendor permission.
